title: Vegan n' Chicken
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Delivery, Take-out, Pakistani, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. In 2015 its changed from Ali Baba Kabab House to Vegan n' Chicken. A small, unassuming restaurant that caters to veg diners by labeling vegan items, which include appetizers, entrees, bread, and at least one dessert. Owner is aware of issues like butter on the bread and milk in the mint chutney.
